 43	cyspbot does not support RFC 8693 `audience`, `actor_token`, or `actor_token_type` form parameters. Non-empty `audience` parameters are rejected with `invalid_target` because this profile uses `resource` for the issued token target and service-owned GitHub App credentials. Actor-token parameters are rejected as malformed for this profile with `invalid_request`.
